The online help contains information on how to use the menus,
various commands, C evaluation expressions and their notes,
information on coprocessors, and startup options.

This help is intended to provide instructions on how to use it, 
and is not intended as instructional guidance
for the source code debugger.

For details, please refer to the "Assembler Manual,"
"Source Code Debugger Manual," "C Compiler User's Manual,"
and "Extended Manual" that come with
the "C Compiler PRO-68K ver2.1 NEW KIT."

